sub_title: Innovation Strategist and Service & Business designer
summary: I am passionate about collaborating with others to help bridge gaps in society by translating complex questions into innovative solutions. I have almost 9 years of experience in designing and implementing large-scale strategic transformations within various (semi-)public sector and healthcare organizations, with a focus on innovation strategy, human-centered design and change management. I believe that co-creation is key in letting solutions thrive, and in adding sustainable value to drive change.
